  * Open Knowledge Format (OKF) v0.1 (GoogleCloudPlatform, Apache-2.0)
    https://github.com/GoogleCloudPlatform/knowledge-catalog
    OKF is the format contract for our wiki/case/pitfall products; it is a
    specification, not code we depend on.
